Pre Show Results

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0989f6a0-df82-4955-bf12-8b511b0cb736/20240526_162457.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_DEONNA PURRAZZO DEF. THUNDER ROSA_**
    

Good match with a lot of stiff striking and heated wrestling. Deonna held the ropes on a roll up to steal the match. A few more minutes and this would’ve been GREAT.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/73553e7e-22d5-4fd1-9156-bcbffd22963b/20240526_163214.jpg?format=original)

Tony Khan and Martha Hart announce the 2024 Owen Hart Cup. Martha Hart asked Tony Khan during a Christmas conversation if the winners could receive World Championship opportunities.

Tony announced not only will they get that, the winners will receive their title shot at AEW ALL IN AT WEMBLY!!!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/43d761f7-0f4e-4559-83ed-f9a87e8a87f5/20240526_170402.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_THE ACCLAIMED DEF. CAGE OF AGONY_**
    

* * *

Main Show Begins.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e5801e13-ce47-4252-ac5d-b8ad1178fecc/20240526_170536.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW INTERNATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP: WILL OSPREAY DEF. RODERICK STRONG(c)_**
    

EXCELLENT match that had a scary beginning when Ospreay tell onto his neck. But they recovered.

Very fun. Don Callis tried to convince Ospreay to use the Tiger Driver but Ospreay couldn’t do it and it almost cost him.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f465bd88-093e-44cc-a84f-01660de71da9/20240526_173009.jpg?format=original)

Adam Cole is out to disrespect Las Vegas but the lights go out. MJF RETURNS.

MJF kicks Adam Cole in the nuts and he makes a proclamation.

## **_“UNLIKE THOSE GUYS IN THE BACK. I DONT NEED A NEW JAPAN OR A VINCE MCMAHON TO MAKE MJF. BECAUSE MJF MADE MJF”_**

MJF says no more love. No more hugs. No more games. He’s back to what drives him the most. He picks up the Devil mask and says it symbolizes a bad time in his career. Then he destroys it.

MJF says he's ALL IN. He shows off an AEW tattoo and confirms he has re-signed.

“You can call me the WOLFE of Wrestling CUZ I AINT FUCKING LEAVING”

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d39fd243-e2c3-434c-aa96-8a650e28dea3/20240526_175323.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW UNIFIED TRIOS CHAMPIONSHIPS: BULLET CLUB GOLD(c) DEF. DEATH TRIANGLE_**
    

Very fun trios match that ends with the return of Juice Robinson!!!! Juice smacks PAC off the turnbuckle, allowing Jay to hit a Bladerunner and win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b6c3aa1c-201c-46d8-970d-a97d1d0ecd58/20240526_180537.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WOMEN'S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: TONI STORM DEF. SERENA DEEB_**
    

Fantastic match. Very physical. Serena Deeb dominates most of the match. At one point, Serena has Toni in the same leg lock that she had Mariah May in when Toni Storm threw in the towel.

Mariah is VERY willing to throw in the towel but Luthor stops her. Toni sees Luthor with the towel and screams at him.

Match ends with an AVALANCHE STORM ZERO PILEDRIVER!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9c4256a2-26d2-489c-ac8e-7daa622a7503/Screenshot_20240526_182502.jpg?format=original)

Orange Cassidy has reverted to "WHERE IS MY MIND" by the Pixies.

He's rocking a black t-shirt for the first time and he's actively enjoying any punishment he gets to lay on Trent Baretta.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7cfe4455-94ac-4a3d-bfd3-b40b162dae92/20240526_183824.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ORANGE CASSIDY DEF. TRENT BARETTA_**
    

This was every bit as heated as if it had a stip attached to it. Real grudge match vibes. The finish sees Orange Cassidy reversing a Triangle into a pin.

Trent Baretta pushes Rocky Romero away. Tells Renee Paquette he’s done. And leaves the building through the audience.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e8ea5894-d506-40ef-a247-b760622c6d2e/20240526_184843.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_FTW RULES TITLE MATCH: CHRIS JERICHO DEF. HOOK AND SHIBATA_**
    

Very interesting match that ends when Bryan Keith costs Hook and Shibata the title. Allowing Jericho to win. Tables, Kendo Sticks, Chairs, Garbage Cans and Dice were used.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fad251cb-45ae-4675-856c-4ac194151f95/20240526_185731.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/53b3ea72-e6db-4e17-b8d2-f3be79560317/20240526_190141.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_IWGP HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP ELIMINATOR MATCH: JON MOXLEY DEF. KONOSUKE TAKESHITA_**
    

Great match that ends when Don Callis coaches Takeshita into a bad play. Takeshita had the match won when Callis said Takeshita should take Mox out with steel chairs.

Takeshita ends up curbstomped onto his very own chair and pinned after a Death Rider.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9968f4f6-f49c-4207-9775-9e2a6459aee7/Screenshot_20240526_190821.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/77962dca-1df3-4572-be54-599904b2e70f/20240526_192705.jpg?format=original)

BROOD ADAM COPELAND IS OUT TO SLAYER'S SOUTH OF HEAVEN!!!!!!!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cd5f8620-89d6-4b0b-b793-2aae4b2882ec/20240526_193403.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_TNT CHAMPIONSHIP BARBED WIRE STEEL CAGE MATCH: ADAM COPELAND(c) DEF. MALAKAI BLACK_**
    

This isn’t the traditional Barbed Wire Steel Cage. There is barbed with inside the cage walls. There are also multiple barbed wire wrapped weapons pre loaded into the cage.

This is every bit as violent as the Hell in a Cell with Finn Balor was supposed to be. House of Black pretended to join Edge before jumping him until GANGREL appeared to fight them off.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/92ac1d7b-8b7a-439c-9e9c-3f60149b6bca/20240526_195134.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0c803179-8a21-4d2f-9770-baa8c34324ff/20240526_202018.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_TBS WOMEN’S CHAMPIONSHIP: MERCEDES MONÉ DEF. WILLOW NIGHTINGALE(c)_**
    

Great match. Mercedes can still go. But she really needs a new finisher.

At one point, Willow had the match won but Mercedes had taunted Statlander and Stokely into distracting the referee.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/182f2094-ee66-475b-ac73-588f728d59c0/20240526_202255.jpg?format=original)

Kris Statlander takes out Stokely Hathaway for being too aggressive with Willow. Then Kris takes out Willow and reveals she is WITH Stokely against Willow 💔

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/aaa159a5-829e-4646-8000-75b30f4337f1/20240526_202816.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f0ce237d-c323-400c-b288-97773d8775d0/20240526_202838.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f83cb938-36f1-48bb-a4ae-b8ddbb0962b3/20240526_202810.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: SWERVE STRICKLAND DEF. CHRISTIAN CAGE_**
    

Swerve Strickland retains by blocking a spear with the HOUSE CALL KICK.

Swerve Stomp, One more house call for the win.

Swerve then goes the celebrate with Floyd Mayweather

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ca134e31-e59a-4899-8f2b-80b6433e1c14/20240526_205704.jpg?format=original)

