![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4bc25d8b-3325-418c-ae33-ff17855b2625/20240526_213005.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ANARCHY IN THE ARENA: THE ELITE DEF. TEAM AEW_**
    

I will never forget what I saw here tonight. Exploding chairs. Thumbtack Facemasks. Thumbtack Rainmakers. Vehicular attempted Homicide. A flamethrower. A Hanging man being treated like a pinata.

Incredible experience. Hell of a way to close a show.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/14321175-f41d-412a-b421-492e641ad574/20240526_212621.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/16c190ca-0fc1-41a9-b243-f3563a7aca05/processed_20240526_212254.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/638b3b28-6321-44ea-8afc-500bad367cfe/Screenshot_20240526_212852.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0a680e69-6186-47e2-a8ad-1438957ecc86/20240526_212902.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/96d11806-e605-4a56-88c6-f8b814bc23b1/Screenshot_20240526_213110.jpg?format=original)